Class DebugVerbosity

java.lang.Object
  test.DebugVerbosity

public class DebugVerbosity
extends java.lang.Object

This class collects all the debug-related variables for classes in this project.
It has not methods, just public static fields that are accessed from within the right destination class.

Author:
Michele Roncalli
